snippet.title: Craft Beer Review Amber Ale Bell's Brewery Holiday Advent Variety Pack Day 12
snippet.description:
This year Bell's Brewery released a Holiday Advent Variety Pack. I have reviewed most of them but let's review all the ones I have not review in 2019. Today's beer is Amber Ale. 

Subscribe here https://goo.gl/uEufrm

If you'd like your beer or brewery to be featured on my channel, I would be glad to feature your product. Please send an email to : 31stbrewing@gmail.com

Check out 31stbrewing.com to keep updated on all things beer
